---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About | Design Leader"
  description="Design Leader at a Fortune 1 retailer. 20 years of UX experience, strategic design, and award-winning work."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <header>
      <h1 class="font-display text-display-lg font-bold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
        About Me
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl font-medium text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]">
        Design Leader at a Fortune 1 Retailer
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-12">
      <section>
        <div class="aspect-square max-w-xs overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-[rgb(var(--color-border))]/30">
          <!-- Placeholder for professional photo - replace with actual image -->
          <div class="flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">
            <span class="text-6xl">Photo</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] prose-p:text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))] prose-a:text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline">
          <p>
            I'm a design leader with 20 years of experience shaping digital experiences that drive
            business outcomes. Currently leading design at a Fortune 1 retailer, I focus on
            strategic direction, team enablement, and cross-functional alignment.
          </p>
          <p>
            My work spans product design, design systems, and organizational design. I've led teams
            through complex transformations—from building design systems that scale across 50+ teams
            to redesigning checkout flows that improved conversion by double digits.
          </p>
          <p>
            I believe design is strategy, not decoration. Every decision should connect to measurable
            impact. I've been recognized with multiple international design awards and am passionate
            about sharing learnings through writing and speaking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Experience</h2>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <li class="border-l-2 border-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]/50 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Design Leader</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]">Fortune 1 Retailer</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">Present</p>
          </li>
          <li class="border-l-2 border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Senior Design roles</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">20 years in UX, product design, and design leadership</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">What I Do</h2>
        <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated))] p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Design Leadership</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">Strategy, vision, and team development</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated))] p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Team Building</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">Hiring, mentoring, and org design</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated))] p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Strategic Design</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">Aligning design with business outcomes</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated))] p-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Cross-Functional Alignment</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">Bringing product, engineering, and business together</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-elevated))] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-display font-bold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">
          Open to speaking, advisory, and consulting opportunities. Reach out to discuss design
          leadership, team building, or how we can collaborate.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@example.com"
          class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-[rgb(var(--color-accent))] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
        >
          Contact Me
        </a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
